WEBVTT

00:00:00.171 --> 00:00:02.835
Your mandate is to develop conflict agility.

00:00:03.816 --> 00:00:09.263
When a team member proposes a solution, demand that they state their claim, provide the supporting evidence,

00:00:09.704 --> 00:00:11.586
and articulate the questions it provokes.

00:00:12.447 --> 00:00:14.410
Treat their explanations as thinking events.

00:00:15.131 --> 00:00:19.997
You must then map the specific variables of the dispute to the correct resolution strategy.

00:00:20.698 --> 00:00:25.565
Problem solving, smoothing, forcing, compromising, or withdrawing.
